@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴通过 OIDC 获取的 access_token
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000

@BrowseHistory_PostId = 在这里填入一个存在的 postId
@BrowseHistory_ProductId = 在这里填入一个存在的 productId
@BrowseHistory_WikiId = 在这里填入一个存在的 wiki documentId
@BrowseHistory_WikiSlug = 可选：在这里填入一个存在的 wiki slug
@Public_UserIdentifier = usr_在这里填入用户PublicId，兼容期也可填旧LongId字符串

### 获取个人资料
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetMyProfile
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 更新个人资料
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/UpdateMyProfile
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "userName": "Radish User",
  "userEmail": "user@example.com",
  "realName": "Radish",
  "age": 18,
  "address": "Asia/Shanghai"
}

### 修改登录密码
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/ChangeMyLoginPassword
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

{
  "currentPassword": "OldPassword1",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword1",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword1"
}

### 访问帖子详情（预期写入 Post 浏览记录）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{BrowseHistory_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 访问商品详情（预期写入 Product 浏览记录）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Shop/GetProduct/{{BrowseHistory_ProductId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 访问 Wiki 详情（按文档 ID，预期写入 Wiki 浏览记录）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetById/{{BrowseHistory_WikiId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 访问 Wiki 详情（按 slug，可选）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetBySlug/{{BrowseHistory_WikiSlug}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取我的浏览记录第一页
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetMyBrowseHistory?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 再次访问帖子详情（预期同一对象 viewCount 增加，而不是新增重复对象）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetById/{{BrowseHistory_PostId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 再次获取我的浏览记录，核对 viewCount / routePath / 最近浏览时间
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetMyBrowseHistory?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取我的浏览记录第二页（可选，验证分页）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetMyBrowseHistory?pageIndex=2&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取公开资料
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetPublicProfile?identifier={{Public_UserIdentifier}}
Accept: application/json

### 通过公开标识获取公开资料统计
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/User/GetPublicUserStats?identifier={{Public_UserIdentifier}}
Accept: application/json

### 通过公开标识获取公开帖子列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Post/GetPublicUserPosts?identifier={{Public_UserIdentifier}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 通过公开标识获取公开评论列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Comment/GetPublicUserComments?identifier={{Public_UserIdentifier}}&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json
